content.13/f Haley 1500/z winter/t 1000 1600: desolate/35 11/farmer 35 3 2 Haley 35 11 2/speed Haley 4/skippable/move Haley -2 0 3/pause 300/faceDirection Haley 2/move Haley 4 0 1/pause 300/faceDirection Haley 0/move Haley -2 0 2/emote Haley 28/move farmer 0 5 2/faceDirection Haley 0/emote Haley 16/speak Haley "@！快来！$s"/move farmer 0 2 2/speak Haley "我的手镯不见了！我来这里的时候还戴着的……$s#$b#但现在消失了，找来找去都找不到……$s"/emote farmer 16/faceDirection farmer 3/faceDirection farmer 1/faceDirection farmer 2/emote farmer 8/speak Haley "$q 48 null#这东西现在已经买不到了……$s#$r 48 -30 Event_beach1#别担心，我给你买个新的！ #$r 48 50 Event_beach2#太遗憾了……"/faceDirection Haley 2/move farmer 1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 600/showFrame Haley 22/pause 500/speak Haley "对不起，曾祖母。我弄丢了你珍贵的手镯。请原谅我。$s"/playMusic ocean/pause 1000/message "会不会是掉在附近了？"/playerControl haleyBeach/globalFade .015/viewport -1000 -1000/warp farmer 36 11/faceDirection farmer 3/positionOffset farmer 0 16/faceDirection Haley 1/pause 500/viewport 35 11 true/pause 800/playMusic sadpiano/speak Haley "那个是……？$8"/emote Haley 16/jump Haley/pause 600/speak Haley "你找到了！$h"/showFrame Haley 23/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/eyes 5 -5000/positionOffset Haley 2 1/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/positionOffset Haley 2 0/pause 50/speak Haley "太感谢你了，@。你真是我的恩人。"/eyes 1 -5000/pause 3000/speak Haley "我不会忘记你的帮忙的。$l"/end dialogue Haley "我欠你一次人情，@。"
content.20/f Alex 500/z winter/p Alex/w sunny: playful/-100 -100/farmer 27 7 2 Alex 25 17 2/showFrame Alex 23/skippable/animate Alex false true 125 16 17 18 19 20 21 22 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23 23/viewport 28 14 true/move farmer 0 10 2/stopAnimation Alex/showFrame Alex 24/pause 600/showFrame Alex 23/speak Alex "嗨。"/pause 300/emote Alex 40/speak Alex "呃，你是@，对吧？"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/speak Alex "我只是在享受这天气，@。"/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 1/pause 500/showFrame Alex 24/speak Alex "嗯……$u#$b#喂，要试玩一下不！$h"/pause 500/move farmer 2 0 3/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 4/animate Alex false false 80 24 25 25 26 4/pause 240/playSound throw/animate farmer true true 100 30/specificTemporarySprite joshFootball/null/pause 500/stopAnimation farmer/pause 700/speak Alex "呵……接得漂亮。"/pause 500/move farmer -2 0 2/pause 800/faceDirection Alex 2/speak Alex "我将会成为星露谷的第一位专业格球选手……我毫不怀疑。#$b#我已经率领校队打入了区域季后赛……现在我只需一直训练加强自己以便获得加入祖祖城隧道队主力队的机会。你等着瞧吧！"/pause 1000/question fork1 "#我相信你！#哇，你真够自大的。"/fork arrogantJosh/faceDirection Alex 1/pause 500/speak Alex "非常感谢，@。我会记住的。"/move Alex 1 0 1/pause 500/end dialogue Alex "嘿，爽不爽啊？"
content.arrogantJosh: pause 500/faceDirection Alex 3/emote Alex 12/faceDirection Alex 2/speak Alex "嗯……有人嫉妒了。$a"/move Alex 0 -15 0 true/speak Alex "我先走了。$a"/faceDirection farmer 0/end dialogue Alex "……$a"
content.288847/f Alex 2000/p Alex/w sunny/G !IS_: ocean/-100 -100/farmer 52 13 2 Alex 53 24 2/showFrame Alex 38/skippable/viewport 53 24 true/pause 2000/speak Alex "*吸气*……$s"/move farmer 0 11 2/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 36/pause 500/showFrame Alex 37/pause 500/speak Alex "哦……@。被你看见我流泪了。$s"/pause 500/showFrame Alex 36/pause 1000/showFrame 95/pause 2000/speak Alex "十二年前的今天……我母亲离开了人间。$9"/pause 1000/speak Alex "我很想念她……她经常做腌萝卜三明治给我们当午餐……经常跟我在后院玩格球。$9#$b#她把我照顾得很好……年轻时不懂得如何说“谢谢”。现在却子欲养而亲不待。$9"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 38/pause 1000/speak Alex "这是我保存下来的唯一信物…………她的秘密音乐盒。$s"/pause 1000/playSound openBox/showFrame Alex 35/pause 500/playMusic tinymusicbox/pause 10000/specificTemporarySprite JoshMom/pause 20000/playMusic ocean/pause 900/showFrame Alex 37/pause 900/showFrame Alex 36/pause 800/speak Alex "$q -1 null#那么……你现在在想什么，@？$9#$r -1 0 event_box1#活出精彩人生以报答你母亲养育之恩。#$r -1 0 event_box2#你不应该沉浸在过去不放手。#$r -1 0 event_box3#要是你寂寞了，我永远会陪伴你。#$r -1 0 event_box4#咬咬牙撑过去。人生不易，且行且珍惜。"/pause 1000/showFrame Alex 36/pause 1000/speak Alex "呆在这里发呆也不算事……咱们回镇子去吧。$9"/showFrame Alex 0/stopAnimation farmer/move Alex 0 -2 0 true/move farmer 0 -2 0 false/pause 1000/faceDirection Alex 3/pause 800/speak Alex "呃……@？$9"/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 1/pause 500/speak Alex "别告诉任何人我哭了，好吗？$7"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/animate farmer false true 100 102 103/pause 100/jump Alex/pause 1500/stopAnimation farmer/move farmer 0 -8 0 true/faceDirection Alex 0/emote Alex 16/speak Alex "嘿！$7"/move Alex 0 -8 0 true/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end
content.29/f Sebastian 2000/t 1200 2300/w rainy: rain/12 38/farmer 12 29 2 Sebastian 12 39 2/skippable/move farmer 0 7 2/faceDirection Sebastian 0/pause 400/speak Sebastian "@？"/pause 500/move farmer 0 2 2/speak Sebastian "嘿，没想到会在雨中遇见你。"/pause 500/faceDirection Sebastian 2/pause 200/move farmer 1 0 2/move farmer 0 1 3/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/playMusic echos/pause 1000/speak Sebastian "你看天边那些乌云……"/pause 2000/speak Sebastian "希望是奔我们而来的。"/faceDirection farmer 3/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Sebastian "我喜欢这种天气，所有人都消失不见……#$b#因为人一多我就感到紧张。$s"/faceDirection Sebastian 1/pause 400/faceDirection Sebastian 2/pause 400/speak Sebastian "不过跟你在一起我没有紧张的感觉。$7"/pause 2000/emote Sebastian 28/speak Sebastian "我们都成落汤鸡了……"/pause 900/showFrame Sebastian 39/animate Sebastian false false 300 37 38 39/pause 300/playSound cast/pause 280/specificTemporarySprite umbrella/pause 800/speak Sebastian "来……这里有足够两人的位置。$7"/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/pause 800/faceDirection farmer 3/animate farmer true true 100 6 7/playSound dwop/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/positionOffset farmer -2 0/pause 100/stopAnimation farmer/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 3500/end
content.43/f Elliott 2500/w sunny/t 700 1300/G !: ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 13 16 2 Elliott 13 27 1/specificTemporarySprite elliottBoat/skippable/viewport 17 26 clamp true/move farmer 0 8 2/faceDirection Elliott 0/speak Elliott "嘿，"/move farmer 0 2 2/faceDirection Elliott 1/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Elliott "话说……我修好了我屋子旁边那艘旧划艇。厉害吧？"/pause 500/faceDirection Elliott 0/pause 500/speak Elliott "@……不知道你是否愿意加入它的首航？$l"/faceDirection farmer 2/question fork1 "是否登上划艇？#是#不是"/fork NoToElliott/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeToTemporaryMap ElliottSea false/playSound wateringCan/pause 1000/playSound wateringCan/playMusic 50s/warp farmer 26 20/positionOffset farmer 0 8/warp Elliott 26 20/showFrame Elliott 25/positionOffset Elliott 0 60/viewport 25 20 true/pause 5000/speak Elliott "我出的书上市一阵子了……虽然销量不算好，但是却获得了专家们的好评。#$b#要不是你的支持和鼓励，我肯定无法完成我的书。$l"/pause 1000/speak Elliott "其实，我是在开玩笑的。就算没有你我自己也能完成这本书。$h#$b#不过我很感激你信任我……和我的梦想。还有，那个……"/pause 500/speak Elliott "呃……@？该怎么说呢……$8"/emote Elliott 40/speak Elliott "我们成为朋友一阵子了……但是我……我不确定自己是否还当你是朋友。$l"/emote farmer 16/speak Elliott "不是！我不是想要跟你断绝关系的意思！$8#$b#事实上……恰恰相反。$l"/pause 1000/emote Elliott 40/pause 500/speak Elliott "让我想想，我该怎么说才对……？$l#$b#晕，我竟然什么都说不出口了……"/playMusic elliottPiano/pause 2500/showFrame Elliott 35/screenFlash 1/warp Elliott 26 20/positionOffset Elliott 24 8/positionOffset farmer -20 16/faceDirection farmer 1 true/showFrame 101/specificTemporarySprite heart 26 20/playSound dwop/pause 1500/startJittering/pause 700/speak Elliott "$q -1 null#@？你在颤抖……$l#$r -1 50 event_boat1#我很开心。#$r -1 -50 event_boat2#你让我整个人都不好了。别这样。"/stopJittering/fork tooBold/pause 1800/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/speak Elliott "我们还是趁刮起南风前回去吧。$l^啊……你刚才的颤抖引来了绯红鱼的注意……我们得马上离开了。$l"/pause 1400/speak Elliott "从这里远眺山谷……终于有一种“家”的感觉了。"/pause 4000/speak Elliott "*唉*……真是累人的一天……$l"/end
content.NoToElliott: emote Elliott 16/pause 800/faceDirection Elliott 1/showFrame Elliott 31/pause 1000/emote Elliott 28/pause 600/speak Elliott "明白了。$7"/move farmer 0 -10 0 true/pause 800/end dialogue Elliott "……$a"
content.733330/f Sam 750/w sunny/t 700 1500/z wi: ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 40 9 2 Sam 41 18 2 Vincent 43 22 2/skippable/animate Vincent false true 500 18 19/specificTemporarySprite beachStuff/viewport 42 19 true/move farmer 0 9 1/faceDirection Sam 3/speak Sam "嗨，@。天气不错吧？"/faceDirection farmer 2/faceDirection Sam 2/pause 800/speak Sam "我只是来看看我弟弟。这种天气带他出来玩玩挺不错的。"/pause 1700/speak Sam "我们父亲也常常在风和日丽时带我们去沙滩玩。$h"/jump Vincent/stopAnimation Vincent/showFrame Vincent 0/pause 1000/move Vincent 0 -4 3/move Vincent -1 0 3/faceDirection Sam 1/faceDirection farmer 1/playMusic desolate/speak Vincent "山姆……？$u"/pause 900/speak Vincent "父亲还会回来吗？$s"/emote Sam 28/showFrame Sam 34/pause 800/speak Sam "那是当然的，文森特。父亲一做好他的事就会尽快赶回来的。$7"/pause 600/speak Vincent "但是我听到很多大人说……我们的部队被打得落花流水。$s"/showFrame Sam 35/pause 1500/speak Sam "不要相信谣言。$8"/showFrame Sam 4/speak Sam "你忘了父亲有多强大吗？他才不会让垃圾戈特洛士兵抓到！你别担心！$a#$b#而且别忘了还有妈妈和我在这里陪你玩。"/playMusic ocean/speak Vincent "好的！"/jump Vincent/pause 1000/move Vincent 1 0 2/showFrame Sam 4 true/faceDirection Sam 2 true/move Vincent 0 4 2/animate Vincent false true 500 18 19/playSound sandyStep/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 3/pause 800/faceDirection Sam 2/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/speak Sam "老实说，我都不知道父亲会不会回来……新闻都播报了。我们的士兵伤亡惨重。$s#$b#但我又怎么能告诉文森特这些事呢？$7"/pause 1000/question null "#对小孩子坦白很重要。#你做得很对。不能让小孩子失去希望。"/emote Sam 40/pause 1000/splitSpeak Sam "你也是这样想的？$7#$b#或许你是对的……这是个残酷的世界，但是孩子们总得知道这个真相。$s~对……孩子们应该把握这个机会拥有一个快乐的童年。"/pause 700/faceDirection Sam 3/faceDirection farmer 1/speak Sam "对了，我有告诉你乐队开始打出名堂了吗？#$b#对！阿比盖尔是个很棒的鼓手。而塞巴斯蒂安非常重视她……$h"/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/end
content.739330/t 600 1710/*n spring_2_1: ocean/-1000 -1000/farmer 28 35 1 Willy 44 35 1/removeQuest 13/addMailReceived NOQUEST_13/skippable/animate Willy false true 250 28 29 30 31/viewport 44 35 true/move farmer 7 0 1/playSound seagulls/move farmer 7 0 1/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/speak Willy "喂，孩子。$u^喂，姑娘。$u#$b#听说镇子上搬来了一位新来的……终于见到你了。$u"/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 1000/stopAnimation Willy/playSound dwop/faceDirection Willy 2 true/pause 50/faceDirection Willy 3/pause 1000/speak Willy "啊…………我还在放松自己，之前出海了整整一个月……$h#$b#那次真是场大丰收啊！我卖了很多鱼。#$b#终于存够钱购买一支新的鱼竿。$h"/move Willy -1 0 3/pause 1000/speak Willy "给，这条旧鱼竿就送给你好了。$h#$b#最重要的是让钓鱼的传统流传下去。也许培养起你的兴趣后，你会光顾我的商店也说不定。$h"/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/pause 500/faceDirection farmer 2/itemAboveHead rod/pause 3300/awardFestivalPrize rod/faceDirection farmer 2/pause 1000/playSound seagulls/move Willy 0 1 2/pause 1000/showFrame Willy 24/pause 1000/speak Willy "这里的水不错。有着各种各样的鱼。"/pause 1000/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy "啊对了。我的店子恢复营业了，有需要的话随时来找我。$h#$b#你捕到什么也可以卖给我。#$b#“能吃的，就能卖”。呵呵。反正我老爸经常这么说的。$h"/pause 500/playSound seagulls/pause 500/move farmer 0 1 2/pause 1000/pause 500/animate Willy false true 250 28 29 30 31/viewport move 1 0 5500/pause 1500/playSound seagulls/pause 1500/playSound seagulls/pause 2000/end position 42 36
content.711130/t 600 1710/f Willy 1500: ocean/30 34/farmer 27 35 1 Willy 30 34 2 Gus -10 -10 0/skippable/addConversationTopic willyCrabs/showFrame Willy 24/move farmer 3 0 0/showFrame Willy 0/pause 800/speak Willy "啊……太好了，你出现了，小伙子。^啊……啊……太好了，你出现了，小姐。#$b#我遇到……遇到一点麻烦，可能需要帮忙……"/faceDirection Willy 3/faceDirection Willy 0/pause 1000/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy "呃……还是直接让你看一下比较好……"/pause 600/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 0/speak Willy "现在深呼吸一次。"/pause 300/playSound doorClose/warp Willy -100 -100/move farmer 0 -1 0/pause 500/playSound doorClose/warp farmer -100 -100/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/changeLocation FishShop/specificTemporarySprite willyCrabExperiment/warp Willy 5 7/faceDirection Willy 0/playMusic ragtime/pause 500/viewport 5 7 true/pause 5000/warp farmer 5 9/playSound doorClose/pause 100/jump farmer/pause 1000/emote farmer 16/faceDirection Willy 3 true/pause 100/faceDirection Willy 2/speak Willy "正如你能看到……#$b#能闻到……呃……#$b#这是老姑娘们昨晚的“狂欢”……呵……$h#$b#我的实验需要一些投入……"/move farmer 0 -1 0/move farmer 2 0 1/emote farmer 56/warp Gus 5 9/playSound doorClose/pause 100/jump Gus/pause 1000/speak Gus "Hooo~……又在做实验，威利？$h"/textAboveHead Willy "对……"/move Gus 0 -1 3/move Gus -2 0 3/pause 1000/speak Gus "它看起来很新鲜……"/faceDirection Willy 3/speak Willy "对……这些是你从未见过的最美味、最肥美的螃蟹。$h#$b#但是，他们有点过于活跃了……$s"/pause 1000/emote Gus 40/pause 500/jump Gus/pause 1000/speak Gus "我全要！$h#$b#当然，额外的人工要打点折……"/pause 2000/move farmer 1 0 0 true/move Gus -1 0 0 false/move farmer 0 -1 0 true/move Gus 0 -1 0 false/faceDirection Willy 0/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 3/pause 1000/playSound slimeHit/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 1/pause 1000/playSound fishSlap/specificTemporarySprite removeSprite 2/pause 500/globalFade/viewport -1000 -1000/pause 1500/speak Gus "似乎全归我们了……"/pause 1000/speak Willy "再见，甜心美人们……$s"/pause 1000/speak Gus "嘘……@……不要告诉威利，但我会在接下来的几天里在酒吧中做点特别的蟹肉饼……"/pause 1000/end position 30 34
content.7771191/t 2000 2500/f Krobus 3500/w sunn: moonlightJellies/-1000 -1000/farmer 0 0 2 Krobus 84 40 2/showFrame Krobus 17/addTemporaryActor SeaMonsterKrobus 32 32 -1 -1 0 false/addLantern 735 83 40 1/positionOffset Krobus 0 52/viewport 84 40 clamp true/pause 3300/animate Krobus false true 500 17 18 17 19/specificTemporarySprite krobusBeach/pause 8000/stopAnimation Krobus/showFrame Krobus 17/pause 2000/emote Krobus 20/pause 4000/faceDirection SeaMonsterKrobus 0/playSound pullItemFromWater/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false false 100 20 21 22 23/warp SeaMonsterKrobus 84 45/pause 600/showFrame Krobus 0/jump Krobus/pause 100/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 250 8 9 10 11/pause 800/pause 1500/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/move SeaMonsterKrobus 0 -3 0/pause 1000/emote Krobus 8/pause 2000/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false false 100 16 17 18 19 19 19 19 19 19 19 19/playSound waterSlosh/pause 400/showFrame SeaMonsterKrobus 19/pause 500/playSound coin/warp Krobus -1 -1/faceDirection SeaMonsterKrobus 2 true/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 500 0 1/pause 2000/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 0 3 2/animate SeaMonsterKrobus false true 500 2 3/pause 3000/stopAnimation SeaMonsterKrobus/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 3 0 1/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus -6 0 3/emote SeaMonsterKrobus 20 true/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus 6 0 1/playSound waterSlosh/move SeaMonsterKrobus -9 0 3 true/pause 2000/fade/viewport -2000 -2000/pause 3000/end
content.3131209/n willyBugWadCutscene: ocean/-2000 -2000/farmer 49 22 2/addTemporaryActor Willy 16 64 52 26 2/addCraftingRecipe Quality Bobber/skippable/specificTemporarySprite WillyWad/animate Willy false true 500 8 9 10 11/pause 1000/speak Willy "嘿嘿……它们很喜欢……看它们动来动去！$h"/pause 1000/playSound slosh/pause 500/playSound slosh/pause 500/playSound slosh/pause 500/viewport 52 24 true/pause 1000/move farmer 0 2 2/textAboveHead Willy "啊嘿！"/pause 2000/speak Willy "我正想到你，小伙子。^我正想到你，小姑娘。#$b#你找到的虫肉真是完美！#$b#哈哈……我说“新鲜”，不是想要还在蠕动的！#$b#啊，我没在抱怨！鱼儿很喜欢……哈哈哈……$h"/emote farmer 28 true/pause 300/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 500/playSound slimeHit/pause 1000/speak Willy "作为感谢，我想教给你一个老渔夫的秘密……我老爹好多年前带我出去钓鱼的时候教我的。"/pause 500/playSound reward/message "已学会制作“优质浮标”"/pause 500/speak Willy "用那个浮标可以吸引来高品质的鱼。#$b#然后口袋里就会有更多的钱，小伙子。哈哈……$h^然后口袋里就会有更多的钱，小姑娘。哈哈……$h"/pause 1500/pause 300/playSound fishBite/pause 500/pause 400/playSound FishHit/animate Willy false true 100 17 18/textAboveHead Willy "钓到了！"/shake Willy 5000/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/playSound slosh/pause 220/playSound slosh/pause 160/playSound slosh/pause 200/fade/viewport -1000 -1000/end
